snippet.title: Figma
snippet.description:
Figma is a free design tool for teams who build products together. Born on the Web, Figma helps the entire product team create, test, and ship better designs, faster.
https://www.figma.com

FigJam is an online whiteboard where teams ideate together. Nothing great is made alone, so sign up for free and start brainstorming with your team!
https://www.figma.com/figjam/
